<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6127634>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Alitropus typus H. Milne Edwards 1840, male (19.0 mm; ZSI/MBRC D1-568). (a–e) Pleopods 1– 5 respectively; (f) right uropod." ;
